OL,3,CThree children and woman 'murdered' in
OL,4,Chouse fire
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after three children and a
OL,8,Fwoman died in a house fire in Bradford.
OL,10,FA 29-year-old woman, later named by
OL,11,Fpolice as Bryonie Gawith, died at the
OL,12,Fscene following the incident on
OL,13,FWestbury Road at 2.07am on Wednesday.
OL,15,FThe children ` Aubree, aged 22 months,
OL,16,Ffive-year-old Oscar and Denisty, nine
OL,17,F` were taken to hospital but later
OL,18,Fdied.
