OL,6,FA 39-year-old man who was found
OL,7,Fcritically injured was arrested at the
OL,8,Fscene on suspicion of murder.
OL,10,FLindsey Pearson, who lives nearby,
OL,11,Fwitnessed the incident unfolding. She
OL,12,Fsaid: "I saw blue flashing lights,
OL,13,Fwhich were just continuous, and
OL,14,Fthought 'something's not right'."
OL,16,FMs Pearson said her daughter and son-
OL,17,Fin-law, who live with her, said their
OL,18,Froom was filled with the smell of
OL,19,Fsmoke.
