OL,6,FShe said: "We looked out of the window
OL,7,Fand just saw a big flame. The sky was
OL,8,Fjust lit up. It was like thunder and
OL,9,Flightning."
OL,11,FMs Pearson, who has lived in the area
OL,12,Ffor 14 years, said: "We thought it was
OL,13,Fthe care home at the top of the road,
OL,14,Fbecause that's where we work, and
OL,15,Fthought 'we need to go, we need to
OL,16,Fgo'."
OL,18,FShe said she left the house with her
OL,19,Fson-in-law and was met with police.
