OL,6,F"They were saying 'there's people
OL,7,Finside, it's a house fire'," she said.
OL,8,F"And they wouldn't let us through,
OL,9,Fwhich you can understand but we just
OL,10,Fwanted to help. It's absolutely
OL,11,Fterrible. Everybody was just so upset."
OL,13,FPeople began to leave flowers at the
OL,14,Fpolice cordon on Wednesday afternoon.
OL,16,FA message with one bunch said: "I love
OL,17,Fyou all, all this world and more. I
OL,18,Fwill miss you forever. Miss you my
OL,19,Fbeautiful angels."
