OL,6,FAround 100m of Westbury Road remained
OL,7,Fcordoned off around the three-bedroom
OL,8,Fsemi-detached house and there were a
OL,9,Fnumber of police vehicles still parked
OL,10,Fin the street.
OL,12,FEarlier, forensics officers in white
OL,13,Fprotective clothing could be seen
OL,14,Fgoing in and out of the property.
OL,16,FDet Ch Insp Stacey Atkinson, of the
OL,17,FHomicide and Major Enquiry Team at
OL,18,FWest Yorkshire Police, said: "This is
OL,19,Fan absolutely devastating incident in
OL,20,Fwhich three children and a woman have
OL,21,Flost their lives.
