OL,6,F"Our thoughts remain with their
OL,7,Ffamily, friends and loved ones.
OL,9,F"Early enquiries show that the fire
OL,10,Fwas started deliberately, and we have
OL,11,Farrested one man on suspicion of
OL,12,Fmurder. He is seriously ill in
OL,13,Fhospital today as a result of injuries
OL,14,Fcaused by the fire.
OL,16,F"While our enquiries are at an early
OL,17,Fstage, we do at this time believe the
OL,18,Fincident is domestic related.
